    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1863-12-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1863-12-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="260"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d260">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Howard</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Jackson</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">St. John,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1863-12-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 9, 1863.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You are instructed by Secretary Seward to use your best efforts to secure
                    detention of Chesapeake and arrest of criminals. I now learn that she will
                    proceed to Shelburne.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>J. Q. HOWARD, <hi rend="italic">United States Consul.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
